These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, mirinda, tea
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, alhambra, montecristo, bluemaster
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person drinking cola and the alhambra-smoker##2
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the bongani-smoker##3
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere between the person drinking tea and the person drinking cola##7
4. the alhambra-smoker is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking tea is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
6. the alhambra-smoker is somewhere to the left of the bongani-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | mirinda | tea       | hot-chocolate | cola        |
| Cigar      | montecristo  | alhambra | bluemaster        | bongani |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
4 different pets are kept: dog, goat, hedgehog, snake
There 4 different types of food: mango, raspberry, peas, pumpkin
1. the person eating pumpkin is somewhere between the person eating peas and the owner of the hedgehog##7
2. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the left of the owner of the dog##5
3. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the right of the person eating pumpkin##5
4. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
5. the person eating pumpkin is between the person eating peas and the person eating raspberry##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Pet     | hedgehog | goat       | snake         | dog     |
| Food   | raspberry   | pumpkin | peas | mango |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, malaysian, german, indonesian
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, dubstep, house, indie
1. the dutch is on the right of the fan of indie##1
2. the fan of indie is somewhere between the fan of dubstep and the fan of classical##7
3. the fan of house is on the left of the indonesian##1
4. the fan of classical is somewhere between the fan of indie and the malaysian##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Nationality   | malaysian | indonesian | german | dutch  |
| Music-Genre   | house | classical  | indie   | dubstep |

