.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, traveling, woodworking, writing
There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, lavender, red, green
1. the person who likes green is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere between the person who likes lavender and the person who's hobby is writing##7
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person who likes green##1
4. the person who likes red is on the left of the person who likes green##1
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who likes purple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Hobby   | traveling | collecting | writing       | woodworking |
| Color   | lavender      | purple   | red | green  |

