.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, engineer, doctor, software-developer
There are 4 different nationalities: american, brazilian, chinese, german
1. the german is on the left or right of the engineer##3
2. the american is somewhere to the left of the brazilian##5
3. the librarian is on the right of the doctor##1
4. the german is somewhere between the engineer and the librarian##7
5. the german is on the left of the chinese##1
6. the brazilian is somewhere to the left of the german##5
7. the engineer is on the far left or far right##3
8. the librarian is on the left or right of the doctor##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Job         | doctor | librarian   | software-developer | engineer |
| Nationality   | american      | brazilian | german      | chinese |

