.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, mirinda, sprite
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, orange, ebony, black
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
2. the person who likes ebony is the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person who likes orange is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person who likes black##3
6. the person who likes black is somewhere between the person who likes red and the person who likes orange##7
7. the person who likes ebony is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | 7up      | mirinda | sprite     |
| Color   | red    | black | orange   | ebony |

