.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-7::.
There 4 different types of food: cherry, grapefruit, orange, pepper
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, subway, taxi, bus
1. the person driving the train is on the far left##1
2. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
3. the person eating pepper is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person driving the bus is somewhere between the person eating cherry and the person eating orange##7
5. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the left of the person eating orange##5
6. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food          | pepper    | cherry   | grapefruit | orange  |
| Transport   | train | taxi | bus    | subway |

