.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, photographer, electrician, dressmaker
4 different pets are kept: dog, hamster, horse, rabbit
1. the photographer is not the owner of the rabbit##6
2. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
3. the dressmaker is the owner of the horse##1
4. the electrician is somewhere between the dressmaker and the lawyer##7
5. the photographer is on the left of the lawyer##1
6. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
7. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Job   | dressmaker | electrician | photographer | lawyer |
| Pet           | horse   | rabbit    | dog       | hamster  |

