.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-9::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, white, azure, blue
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, pop, r&b, techno
1. the person who likes lavender is not the fan of classical##6
2. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
3. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the person who likes lavender##3
4. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the fan of techno##1
5. the person who likes azure is somewhere between the fan of techno and the person who likes white##7
6. the fan of pop is somewhere to the right of the fan of r&b##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |       4        |
| Color           | blue | lavender | azure | white |
| Music-Genre   | techno         | r&b      | classical | pop            |

