The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, sailing, skiing, tennis
1. the person who's sport is climbing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is tennis##5
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
3. the person who's sport is tennis is not the person driving the ship##6
4. the person driving the car is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
5. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is climbing##5
6. the person driving the roller is somewhere between the person driving the ship and the person driving the car##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |      3      |    4    |
| Transport   | car | roller | helicopter | ship |
| Sport   | tennis  | sailing    | climbing    | skiing  |

