2. the fisherman is the person driving the bike##1
3. the person driving the subway is the lawyer##1
4. the lawyer is not the person driving the bus##6
5. the lawyer is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
6. the person driving the bus is somewhere between the person driving the bike and the lawyer##7
7. the architect is somewhere to the left of the person driving the subway##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |
