.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-14::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, mirinda, water
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, november, april, january
1. the person who's birthday is in november is in an even position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere between the person drinking water and the person who's birthday is in april##7
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
4. the person who's birthday is in april is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in november##5
6. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
7. the person drinking fanta is the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |
| Beverage      | cola   | mirinda | fanta | water   |
| Birthday   | december | april   | january | november |

