1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who likes light-blue##7
2. the person who likes purple is somewhere to the right of the person who likes coral##5
3. the person who likes light-blue is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not the person who likes light-blue##6
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere between the person who likes purple and the person who likes green##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby   | skydiving | sudoku     | drawing     | rock-climbing |
| Color     | light-blue | green | coral | purple     |

